类 AbstractMultimap<K,V,C extends java.util.Collection<V>>

    public abstract class AbstractMultimap<K,V,C extends java.util.Collection<V>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Map<K,C>
    Combines a Map with List values to provide simple way to store multiple values for a key (multimap).

    Threading note: All methods are synchronized
